07/11/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- US State Secretary Colin Powell sent a letter Thursday (6 November) praising reforms in Albania over the past year and predicting more of the same in the future.
In other news, European Parliament (EP) Speaker Patrick Cox described last month's local elections as a step forward and pledged EP support for Albania on its road to EU integration.
(ATA, Albanian Radio, BBC - 06/11/03)
